VACUUM
</programlisting></para>
 </refsect1>

 <refsect1>
  <!--
<title>Compatibility</title>
-->
<title>兼容性</title>

  <!--
<para>
   There is no <command>VACUUM</command> statement in the SQL standard.
  </para>
-->
<para>
SQL 标准里没有<command>VACUUM</command>语句。
</para>
